Gminer v2.40
* significant performance improvements for KawPoW, especially on rigs with large number of GPUs
* improved compatibility with Ravencoin pools
* added option to control DAG buffering mode single or dual via option `--dag_mode`
* added option to support "Zombie Mode" for Ethash, Etchash and KawPoW algortihms via option `--dag_limit`
* improved detection of freezing AMD GPUs
* fixed display of core and memory clocks
* display GPU PCI index on miner startup
* removed unpopular algorithms: sero, vprogpow, progpowz, cuckarood29, cuckarood29v

